ex1) Adaboost (Adaptive Boost)¶

: weak learner , weak learner . M M .

, .

Adaboost의 기본 형태¶

m weak learner $f_{m}$ .
$f_{m}$ $as_{m}=\frac{1}{2}ln(\frac{1-e_{m}}{e_{m}})$.
($e_{m}$ , $f_{m}$ .)

  • ($y_{i}\cdot f_{m}<0$), $w_{i}^{m+1}=exp(as_{m})$
  • ($y_{i}\cdot f_{m}>0$), $w_{i}^{m+1}=exp(-as_{m})$

m+1 .


[ $f_{m}$ ] $\to$ [ $e_{m}$ $as_{m}$ ] $\to$ [ ] $\to$ [ n ]

M $\widehat{h}=sign(\sum_{i=1}^{M}as_{i}\cdot f_{i})$ .

Adaboost에서 사용되는 손실함수¶

일반적인 지수(Exponential) 손실함수¶

$y_{i}=\left\{-1,1 \right\}$, $h$ , $h^{*}$
$$l=exp(-yh)$$
, $$\frac{\partial L}{\partial h}=-yexp(-yh)$$
h $\mathbf{x}_{i}$

$$E(-y \textit{exp}(-yh)|\mathbf{x}_{i})=-\textit{exp}(-h)P(y=1|\mathbf{x}_{i})+\textit{exp}(h)P(y=-1|\mathbf{x}_{i})=0$$

h $$h^{*}=\frac{1}{2}log\frac{P(y=1|\mathbf{x}_{i})}{P(y=-1|\mathbf{x}_{i})}$$ .

$\therefore $ $P(y=1|\mathbf{x}_{i})>0.5$ $h^{*}(\mathbf{x}_{i})>0$ . $\mathbf{x}_{i}$ $y_{i}$ 1 .

Adaboost에서의 지수 손실함수¶

. $$\sum_{i=1}^{n}exp(y_{i}(h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})+\beta(\mathbf{x}_{i})))$$ $$=\sum_{i=1}^{n}exp(-y_{i}h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i}))\cdot exp(-y_{i}\beta f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))$$ $exp(-y_{i}h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i}))$ $w_{i}^{(m)}$ .

$h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})$ (m-1) $y_{i}$ .
, $h_{m-1}=sign(\sum_{i=1}^{m-1}as_{i}\cdot f_{i})$.
$h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})$ $y_{i}$ $y_{i}h_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})<0$ $w_{i}^{(m)}$ .
(m-1) .
m $\beta$ $f$ .

, $y_{i}$ $$ =\sum_{y_{i}=f(\mathbf{x}_{i})}w_{i}^{(m)}e^{-\beta}+\sum_{y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i})}w_{i}^{(m)}e^{\beta}$$ $$=\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}e^{-\beta}(1-I(y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))) + \sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}e^{\beta}I(y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))$$ $$=(e^{\beta}-e^{-\beta})\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}I(y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))+e^{-\beta}\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}$$ , $\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}I(y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))$ .

weak learner $f(\mathbf{x}_{i})$ .
$\beta_{m}=\frac{1}{2}log\frac{1-e_{m}}{e_{m}}=as_{m}$
$e_{m}=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}I(y_{i}\neq f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))}{\sum_{i=1}^{n}w_{i}^{(m)}}$

from sklearn.ensemble import AdaBoostClassifier
ada_t=AdaBoostClassifier(DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=2), n_estimators=500, random_state=1)
ada_t.fit(X_train, y_train)
y_train_pred=ada_t.predict(X_train)
y_test_pred=ada_t.predict(X_test)

from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
ada_train=accuracy_score(y_train, y_train_pred)
ada_test=accuracy_score(y_test, y_test_pred)

print("Adaboost train/test accuracy %0.3f/%0.3f" %(ada_train, ada_test))

ex2) GBM (Gradient Boosting Method)¶

: . weak learner weak learner (residual error) .

$\star$
$$b(\mathbf{x},\gamma)=\sum_{j=1}^{J}\gamma_{j}I(\mathbf{x}\in R_{j})$$
$J$:
$\gamma_{i}$ : j $y_{i}$
$R_{j}$ : $\gamma_{j}$
$R_{j}$ $y_{i}$ , $R_{j}$ $y_{i}$ $\gamma_{j}$
$\gamma_{j}$ $R_{j}$

GBM (M) (J).
J $4\leq J \leq8$

GBM 알고리즘¶

  1. $\sum_{i=1}^{n}l(y_{i},\gamma)$ $f_{0}(\mathbf{x}_{i})=\gamma$
  2. m=1 M
    (a) $g_{im}=[\frac{\partial l(y_{i},f(\mathbf{x}_{i}))}{\partial f(\mathbf{x}_{i})}]_{f=f_{m-1}}$
    (b) J $R_{jm}$ , $$\sum_{i=1}^{n}(-g_{im}-\sum_{j=1}^{J}\gamma_{jm}I(\mathbf{x}_{i}\in R_{jm}))^{2}$$ $\widehat{\gamma}_{jm}$ .
    (c) $\sum_{i=1}^{n}l(y_{i},f_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})+\eta_{m}\sum_{j=1}^{J}\widehat{\gamma}_{jm}I(\mathbf{x}_{i}\in R_{jm}))$ $\eta_{m}$
    (d) $f_{m}(\mathbf{x}_{i})=f_{m-1}(\mathbf{x}_{i})+\widehat{\eta}_{m}\sum_{j=1}^{J}\widehat{\gamma}_{jm}I(\mathbf{x}_{i}\in R_{jm})$
  3. $\widehat{f}(\mathbf{x}_{i})=f_{M}(\mathbf{x}_{i})$

from sklearn.ensemble import GradientBoostingRegressor
gbrg=GradientBoostingRegressor(n_estimators=120, max_depth=3)  # 120  ,   3
gbrg.fit(X_train, y_train)                                     #  
errors=[mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred) for y_pred in gbrg.staged_predict(X_test)]
bst_n_estimators=np.argmin(errors)                             #  MSE  M .
